d point in the kill ring.=0A11-- Ctrl-y : yank=0A12-- Ctrl-w Ctrl-s : Save =
buffer=0A13-- Ctrl-w Ctrl-w <file name> : Save as=0A14-- Ctrl-x Ctrl-f : Vi=
sit file=0A15-- Ctrl-t : Execute OCaml funcion on text=0A16-- Ctrl-r : Togg=
